										Anesthesia & Critical Care

Baxter is a leading manufacturer of products for general anesthesia. These include anesthetic gases, or inhaled anesthetics, and anesthesia-related critical care drugs. 

 







										BioSurgery

Baxter's BioSurgery business unit offers a comprehensive line of biologics, devices and combination products.

 







										Drug Delivery

Baxter is one of the world's leading manufacturers of commercially prepared IV solutions in flexible containers. Baxter also has a range of irrigation solutions and sets to suit a wide range of patient needs.

 







										Infusion Systems

Large Volume Pumps (LVP) are used to deliver medication and solutions through various routes (e.g. Intravenous and epidural) for therapeutic and diagnostic purposes. They are designed for more accurate fluid delivery than manually adjusted gravity infusions. 

 







										Access

Baxter's comprehensive Access portfolio includes Pump Administration sets, Gravity Sets, and ONE-LINK Neutral Displacement Needleless Connector.  Baxter’s Access portfolio offers a variety of different components and configurations to meet a broad range of clinical applications.

 







